'''Anfa''' neɣ '''Taddart Tumlilt''' (es [[Tafrensist|Tefṛansist]] ed tulayin tiyaḍ: "Casablanca", es tutlayt [[Taɛṛabt]]: "الدار البيضاء") d-iɣṛem ameqqṛan akk di tmurt en [[Murakuc]] (Merruk). Zeddɣen deg-s 5 melyun en yimdanen. Anfa d-iɣṛem ameqqran akk deg [[Tamazɣa]] aked Dzayer-Tamanaɣt.

Tella deg '''Anfa''' yiwet tmezgida tameqqṛant isem ines Timezgida Ḥasan Wiss 2.

== Tarakalt ==
anfa yella deg tesga en Anfa-Ẓeṭṭaṭ di tmurt en [[Murakuc]] (Merruk).

